==Bosnian==
===Idiom===
'''mirna Bosna'''
# literally: peacefull Bosnia
# an outcome of an event in which all parties involved are satisfied
#: ''Podijelićemo pare jednako i '''mirna Bosna''''' (We will split the money in equal shares and everybody will be happy)
